<br>
1. You can't cast regular spells, sit and med.<br>
2. You can use right click effects then sit and med while they cast.<br>
<br>
A. Right click the item with an effect<br>
B. Use the /sit command<br>
C. Before the spell is supposed to go off, use a /sit off command<br>
<br>
Time B+C on a social, and you're set.<br>
